text: <!channel> Last I heard we were pushing for delivery "by the end of the month". Since that's this week, I feel we should round up ASAP and figure out what items *need* to be fixed *when* they need to be fixed by, and *what else* we should work on before that time in case we finish all the "need-to"s.
or at the very least I'd like a more concrete notion of what the deadline is
